You’ve posted WAY TOO MANY TIMES about this. -.-

LOOK THROUGH OTHER POSTS? This has been answered at least 5 times today.

Please post something helpful, even if this has been answered, maybe he didn’t understand.

Where every player starts out:

Open Player.java and search:

	// initial x and y coordinates of the player

then under you will see something like:
toX = ####
toY = %%%%

Change those, to the coords you want. Save, Compile Done.
